This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with pattern learning in Natural Language Processing (NLP). It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as these fields are closely related to NLP and pattern learning. Additionally, the paper involves theoretical analysis and approximation algorithms, which could place it in the sub-categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
